The paper deals with the analysis of a wireless communication system, specifically the DS-CDMA cellular downlink. This falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also involves modeling and simulation of the system, which could fall under the categories of simulation and modeling (cs.SI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses resource allocation policies and fairness, which could fall under the category of game theory (cs.GT).
